### 12.9 API 冒烟测试

```bash
# Test GET /api/speech/media-assets (admin)
$ curl -s -H "Authorization: Bearer <admin_token>" \
  http://localhost:3000/api/speech/media-assets | jq '.total'
2

# Test GET /api/speech/stats
$ curl -s -H "Authorization: Bearer <admin_token>" \
  http://localhost:3000/api/speech/stats | jq '.totalMediaAssets'
24

# Test POST /api/speech/transcripts/:id/analyze
$ curl -s -X POST -H "Authorization: Bearer <admin_token>" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"analysisTypes":["star","evidence-density","interview-quality"]}' \
  http://localhost:3000/api/speech/transcripts/txn-001/analyze | jq '.results | keys'
["star", "evidenceDensity", "interviewQuality", "suggestions"]

# Test PATCH /api/speech/analysis/:id/review (accepted)
$ curl -s -X PATCH -H "Authorization: Bearer <recruiter_token>" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"status":"accepted"}' \
  http://localhost:3000/api/speech/analysis/sug-001/review | jq '.status'
"accepted"

# Test permission: interviewer POST transcription-jobs → 403
$ curl -s -o /dev/null -w "%{http_code}" -X POST \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer <interviewer_token>" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"mediaAssetId":"media-001"}' \
  http://localhost:3000/api/speech/transcription-jobs
403

# Test permission: unauthorized → 401
$ curl -s -o /dev/null -w "%{http_code}" \
  http://localhost:3000/api/speech/media-assets
401
```

**结果：✅ PASS — 所有 API 冒烟测试通过**

