### 12.10 红线验证

```bash
# 验证无 fake transcript 文件
$ grep -r "fake.transcript\|mock.transcript\|FakeTranscript\|MockTranscript" \
  app/ server/ --include="*.ts" --include="*.tsx" 2>/dev/null | wc -l
0

# 验证无情绪识别代码
$ grep -r "emotion\|sentiment\|情绪\|情感" \
  app/ server/ --include="*.ts" --include="*.tsx" 2>/dev/null | wc -l
0

# 验证无口音评价代码
$ grep -r "accent\|pronunciation\|口音\|发音" \
  app/ server/ --include="*.ts" --include="*.tsx" 2>/dev/null | wc -l
0

# 验证无性格判断代码
$ grep -r "personality\|character\|性格\|人格" \
  app/ server/ --include="*.ts" --include="*.tsx" 2>/dev/null | wc -l
0

# 验证无自动录用/淘汰代码
$ grep -r "auto.reject\|auto.accept\|自动淘汰\|自动录用\|auto.hire" \
  app/ server/ --include="*.ts" --include="*.tsx" 2>/dev/null | wc -l
0

# 验证无 API Key 硬编码
$ grep -r "sk-\|OPENAI_API_KEY\|DEEPSEEK_API_KEY" \
  app/ components/ --include="*.ts" --include="*.tsx" 2>/dev/null | wc -l
0

# 验证无 PII 硬编码
$ grep -rE "1[3-9][0-9]{9}|[0-9]{17}[0-9Xx]|@[a-zA-Z0-9]+\.[a-zA-Z]+" \
  app/ components/ server/services/ --include="*.ts" --include="*.tsx" 2>/dev/null | wc -l
0
```

**结果：✅ PASS — 所有红线检查通过，0 违规**

